. Lateral view of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" genus="Melidia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melidia claudiae" order="Orthoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="claudiae">Melidia claudiae</taxonomicName>
sp. n. (26), lateral view of 
