holotype (27), cerci and sub-genital plate of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" genus="Melidia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melidia brunneri" order="Orthoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brunneri">Melidia brunneri</taxonomicName>
from Namibia (28), cerci and sub-genital plate of 
